當前嘅環境係咪適合行動。當然有行動有目的我一定會全力支持，但希望大家記得梁天琦所講：不要被仇恨支配自己。我知道前線都係有腦嘅，如果我嘅諗法有錯請屌醒我。<br />\n<br />\n無入你所講嘅勇武group，次次都係獨行。"},{"pid":"23195f0293c9284a6b9f4655fab977c86e9c188b","tid":1503652,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a93adce27bc4fb4cda2984acfb52d8f1ff21bba","tid":1503652,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}